NAME
    App::perl::highlight - Syntax highlight your source code

VERSION
    version 0.001

AVAILABILITY
    The development version lives at
    <http://github.com/doherty/App-perl-highlight> and may be cloned from
    <git://github.com/doherty/App-perl-highlight.git>. Instead of sending
    patches, please fork this project using the standard git and github
    infrastructure.

BUGS AND LIMITATIONS
    Please help me improve readability in the terminal, the colours used
    currently are perhaps not ideal.

    No bugs have been reported.

    Please report any bugs or feature requests through the web interface at
    <http://github.com/doherty/App-syntax-highlight/issues>.

AUTHOR
